{"data":[{"date":"08:15 13/07","title":"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi Juve, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t s\u1ed5 g\u1ea1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/vua-toi-juve-ronaldo-da-khien-dong-doi-buon-nhu-mat-so-gao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 t\u1ea1i Juve. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o \u2013 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCuadrado mi\u1ec7ng c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed5 trong tim<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 7 ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 CR7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Javier Pastore ph\u1ea3i trao s\u1ed1 \u00e1o cho Neymar t\u1ea1i PSG, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Juan Cuadrado c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i cay \u0111\u1eafng d\u00e0nh cho Ronaldo s\u1ed1 7 y\u00eau th\u00edch, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 <strong>&ldquo;nh\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean Instagram, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo; c\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 v\u1edbi t\u00ean Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng t\u00e2n binh t\u1edbi Juventus.<em> &ldquo;Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng anh trong cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi n\u00e0y&rdquo; </em>&ndash; Cuadrado vi\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Juventus s\u1ebd trao chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Ronaldo b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 Cuadrado c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd hay kh\u00f4ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a n\u00e0y, c\u00f9ng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i m\u00e0 Cuadrado kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00ean vui hay bu\u1ed3n: <em>&ldquo;Qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. </em><strong><em>T\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean trao \u0111i, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;</em></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Cuadrado-bi-Ronaldo-lot-ao-Nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus v\u00e0 b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nNgay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Paulo Dybala \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;nh\u1ea3y&rdquo; v\u00e0o troll ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i:<strong> &ldquo;Th\u00f4i n\u00e0o, h\u00e3y th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt \u0111i. Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?&rdquo;</strong>, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rdquo; Cuadrado v\u1eabn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn anh: <em>&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m theo b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. <strong>Quan tr\u1ecdng g\u00ec </strong>m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00e1o sau l\u01b0ng, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111eo s\u1ed1 588.&rdquo;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o &ldquo;trong h\u00f2a b\u00ecnh&rdquo;, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i, CR7 th\u1eeba bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Juve.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec&hellip; Messi?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United &ndash; Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4176","checkdouble":"191069"},{"date":"08:52 13/07","title":"Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi TBN, CLB Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng cho BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Real mua Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard\" title=\"Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/eden-hazard-xem-nhe-chien-thang-cua-dt-phap.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Real mua Hazard sau khi \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Eden Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u1edf \u0110T B\u1ec9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec The Blues r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi Hazard hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi CLB Barca th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Hazard, CLB Real \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. Ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Hazard trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1 s\u1ed1c cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0 Hazard.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Real s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thay m\u00e1u m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a HLV Julen Lopetegui. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real s\u1ebd th\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 Gatreth Bale l\u1eabn Karim Benzema \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4175","checkdouble":"191070"},{"date":"07:02 13/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/tan-hlv-emery-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 SV\u0110 Emirates 5 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn (tr\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o). Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111em v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Stephan Lichtsteiner, trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o &ndash; tr\u1eeb khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1edbn. Emery cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0o. Ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua th\u00eam 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, CLB \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Arsenal-tuyen-bo-chot-so-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ho\u1eb7c sang \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Ramsey, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c Ramsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. N&rsquo;Zonzi? T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i N&rsquo;Zonzi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Wenger, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean mua s\u1eafm ngay s\u00e1t deadline, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery &ndash; c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span><br>\r\nGi\u1eefa l\u00fac World Cup 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1nh chi\u1ebfm th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Torreira m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span><br>\r\nSau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd Arsenal ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4174","checkdouble":"191065"},{"date":"07:17 13/07","title":"Gia nh\u1eadp MLS, Rooney t\u1ed1 Everton ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/gia-nhap-mls-rooney-to-everton-phu-bac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u2013 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton khi \u0111\u1ea9y anh sang M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2>Rooney gia nh\u1eadp MLS<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, G\u00e3 Shrek \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang DC United, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Rooney th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Everton v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 CLB th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Rooney.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Merseyside b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Marco Silva, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 Rooney &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 anh ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a CLB \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t \u0111i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Rooney \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u00f9ng DC United, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 cho vui r\u1eb1ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton sau khi gia nh\u1eadp MLS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton sau khi gia nh\u1eadp MLS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/roon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everon sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MLS</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean ESPN v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Wayne Rooney cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf Man United, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u1eb3ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec. Tuy v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Everton.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00fd do \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 g\u00ec. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00f9 ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MLS&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Everton r\u1eb1ng, nghe n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ebb con. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ra \u0111i, h\u00e3y n\u00f3i r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec h\u00e3y cho t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft. Sau c\u00f9ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp DC United v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co-184-190307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co-184-190307.html\">V\u1eeba sang DC United, Rooney nh\u1eadn vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3</span><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh &ndash; Wayne Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho ng\u00e0y 2/7 h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi-172-189906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi-172-189906.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Rooney x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4173","checkdouble":"191066"},{"date":"07:50 13/07","title":"V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d tung tr\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-mahrez-da-no-tung-troi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2>Mahrez tung Man xanh l\u00ean m\u00e2y<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba qua m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i Leicester City, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00e3 to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n sang Etihad. Riyad Mahrez l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a CLB, khi gia nh\u1eadp Man City v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vui m\u1eebng khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea1 khi Mahrez li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh cho Man City nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c r\u1ea5t s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man xanh, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng &ldquo;ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 thua&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u0103m 2016 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Man City, sau khi th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. <strong>Man City h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/mahrez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man City, b\u1edfi b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (Leicester) ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Man City c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfn xa. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&rdquo; &ndash; Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\">&ldquo;Bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nMan City mua Riyad Mahrez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man xanh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4172","checkdouble":"191068"},{"date":"15:58 12/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Juventus l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/del-pierro-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Juventus, Alessandro Del Piero \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 CR7.</h2><h2>Del Pierro l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Del Pierro l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Del Pierro l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Del-Pierro-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh nh\u01b0 Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB&nbsp;Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 Real v\u00e0 Juve x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo sang Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 ngo\u00e0i 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 CR7, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 19 n\u0103m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi 'B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0', danh th\u1ee7 Alessandro Del Piero \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Juve, v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111ang n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Juve, v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa h\u00ednh, khi\u1ebfn Serie A tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. T\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus chi ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Anh ta lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng CLB m\u00e0 anh ta kho\u00e1c \u00e1o. Juventus \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Ronaldo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 k\u1ebb b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1edbi 7 danh hi\u1ec7u Scudetto li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong 7 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua song Juve v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 1995/96. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 Bianconeri l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\">10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n chia ch\u00e1c khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Real Madrid n\u0103m 2009, nh\u01b0ng MU v\u1eabn thu v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n sau khi Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4171","checkdouble":"191043"},{"date":"19:37 12/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7: MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 ch\u00e0ng Cristiano kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Sporting","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7.</h2><h2>MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Cristiano Piccini\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 127 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 127 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/193510-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7: Cristiano Piccini l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Turkish Football  \u0111\u01b0a tin Man United \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi West Ham \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a  h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Cristiano Piccini. Besiktas \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh pole trong  th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3n  Piccini v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sporting s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t  m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1eefa gi\u1ed1ng Cristiano Ronaldo n\u0103m x\u01b0a.</div>\r\n<h2>Marcelo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juve</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Corriere della Sera, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus c\u00f9ng Ronaldo. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Marcelo l\u00e0 Jorge Mendes \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1edbi Juventus. N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arthur Melo nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Griezmann. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mong mu\u1ed1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Hazard n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ebf t\u1eafc khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Grizou.</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Tuttosport \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u00e0 Juve mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 Diego Godin, Stefan Savic, Shkodran Mustafi v\u00e0 Juan Bernat. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Daniele Rugani \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi th\u00e0nh Turin, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Medhi Benatia v\u00e0 Alex Sandro \u0111ang m\u00f4ng lung, &ldquo;L\u00e3o b\u00e0&rdquo; bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00eam kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>PSG theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u01b0a tin, PSG \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00e0 Rhian Brewster. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-117-xac-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-184-190977.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 11/7: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1007-mu-di-nuoc-co-quan-trong-vu-sao-100-trieu-euro-184-190873.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/07: MU \u0111i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ee5 sao 100 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4170","checkdouble":"191057"},{"date":"06:11 13/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7: Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 13/7.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Anh nh\u01b0 BBC, Telegraph \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin HLV Antonio Conte s\u1ebd r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u00e1m \u01a1n t\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7 Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 137 Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-Conte-da-bi-Chelsea-sa-thai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7: Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Willian. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng sau khi Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho M.U</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 - Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Man United v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail, Spurs s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nHarry Maguire &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 Wolrd Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Chelsea v\u00e0 M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Leicester. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Ruyad Mahrez, v\u00ec v\u1eady h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Harry Maguire\" title=\"Harry Maguire vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111em v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 - \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Torreira, Guendouzi, Lichtsteiner, Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 Leno.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4169","checkdouble":"191062"},{"date":"06:36 13/07","title":"Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec\u2026 Messi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United \u2013 Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2>Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juve v\u00ec Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u, Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00ean x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. CR7 nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do r\u1eddi Real Madrid, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ryan Giggs c\u0169ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169, khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Wales cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb1ng sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7 l\u00e0 do n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1eddi Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn Italia&rdquo; &ndash; Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo. &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u1ed5n v\u00ec Juventus c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, Man United v\u00e0 Juventus, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo V\u00ec Messi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo V\u00ec Messi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Ryan-Giggs-chia-se-ve-Ronaldo-Vi-Messi,-cau-ay-phai-toi-Juve-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng bom t\u1ea5n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Messi. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Messi \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Italia &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ngh\u0129. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. <strong>C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Messi.&rdquo;</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, HLV \u0110T x\u1ee9 Wales c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Gareth Bale: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t Bale n\u1eefa. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Neymar ho\u1eb7c Mbappe. Real \u0111ang c\u00f3 100 tri\u1ec7u euro trong t\u00fai v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/Ryan-Giggs-chia-se-ve-Ronaldo-Vi-Messi,-cau-ay-phai-toi-Juve-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\">10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: &ldquo;K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United, Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Jose Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4168","checkdouble":"191064"},{"date":"20:39 12/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/chinh-thuc-barca-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-clement-lenglet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>(ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lenglet v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lenglet v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/CHINH-THUC-Barca-chieu-mo-Lenglet-voi-gia-35-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mua xong Lenglet</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/top-5-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-tiem-nang-cua-barca-trong-he-2018-184-184650.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet</span> t\u1eeb Sevilla. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Barca ph\u1ea3i chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda Sevilla. Trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Lenglet k\u00fd v\u1edbi Barcelona c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Lenglet su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p d\u00e0nh cho Los Blaugrana. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0La Liga \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Lenglet v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11, c\u00e1c tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Lenglet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Camp Nou. Khi tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u00e0o m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lenglet \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Sevilla c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn Lenglet th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Ramon Sanchez Pizjuan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Lenglet v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Sevilla v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Barca ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<h2>Lenglet l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Sevilla t\u1eeb Nancy v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017, Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u0103n \u0111u\u1ed5i. Man United c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Lenglet nh\u01b0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp theo gia nh\u1eadp Barca sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ousmane Dembele, Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Sevilla, Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n 70 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 10 l\u1ea7n \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U21. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Lenglet c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb t\u1eeb U16 \u0111\u1ebfn U21.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4167","checkdouble":"191060"},{"date":"18:58 12/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: H\u00e0ng hot Ligue 1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jean Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi NHM b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fulham ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Jean Michael Seri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 h\u00f4m b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jean Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh London. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Chelsea, b\u1edfi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jean Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jean Michael Seri t\u1edbi Fulham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Stamford Bridge mu\u1ed1n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/so-arsenal-vuot-mat-chelsea-day-nhanh-toc-do-mua-xavi-chau-phi-172-186930.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Chelsea mua Michael Seri</span>, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal, Emery trong th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Ligue 1 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. Jean Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fulham, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Craven Cottage.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Fulham. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cFulham vui m\u1eebng khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022 v\u1edbi Michael Seri, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Tony Khan c\u1ee7a Fulham th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Michael Seri, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho Fulham\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Michael Seri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Fulham</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Fulham, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Michael Seri c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean Michael Seri tung la muc tieu cua Chelsea va Arsenal\" title=\"Jean Michael Seri t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/sari.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jean Michael Seri h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi t\u1edbi Fulham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Fulham, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 CLB c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u1edf Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Fulham, hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4166","checkdouble":"191053"},{"date":"20:27 12/07","title":"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau MU sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Perisic t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi b\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u00f4m h\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Perisic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u00f4m h\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perisic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00f4m qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n su\u00fdt gi\u00fap cho Croatia th\u1eafng ngay trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pickford nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2, Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T\u00a0Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng Man United \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Inter y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn Perisic tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 nhanh v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Nh\u01b0ng Perisic c\u00f2n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u1ecfe n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng tranh b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Perisic gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Mandzukic ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic, HLV Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez. V\u00e0 x\u00e9t theo nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Sanchez \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic-421-191055.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Croatia 2-1 Anh: Cu\u1ed9c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e2n x\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4165","checkdouble":"191059"},{"date":"14:53 12/07","title":"T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eebng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/tong-thong-croatia-dien-mung-thay-tro-dalic.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4164","checkdouble":"191033"}]}